headline: Calling All Trailblazers: Introducing the Inaugural "PropTech Startup Showdown" at SXSW 2026
summary: Calling all innovators, on March 13th Realtor.com® and National Association of REALTORS® Tech & Innovation are teaming up at SXSW to launch the first PropTech Startup Showdown. The inaugural PropTech Startup Showdown at SXSW will be a high-energy competition designed to identify and elevate the next generation of real estate technology innovators.
